SOURCE:
set server "example.com"
set port 8080
enable logging

task "backup_files"
on event "daily_backup"
execute "run_backup.sh"

select name, age
from users
where age > 18

create button "Submit"
align center
set color "blue"

if temperature > 30
then set fan_speed "high"
else set fan_speed "low"

source "data.csv"
transform "normalize"
output "cleaned_data.csv"

allow user "admin"
access resource "settings"
deny user "guest"

notify email "user@example.com"
on event "file_uploaded"
with message "Your file has been uploaded successfully."

create vlan 10
assign ip "192.168.1.1"
enable dhcp

test "LoginFunctionality"
input username "user1"
expect status "success"

def calculate
    result = 3 ** 2
    print result
end

square x -> x * x
print square(4)

create_file "notes.txt"
write_to "notes.txt" "Hello, DSL!"
